        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "literal": "The issues of gimbal lock and difficulties in interpolation with Euler angles are highlighted."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
